Distribution: In the Pacific Ocean known from Indonesia , Philippines , Papua New Guinea , and the South China Sea ( Kramp, 1968 ; Bouillon, 1984b ;
Wang et al ., 2018
); in the Indian Ocean from the Mozambique Channel ( Kramp, 1957 ); in the Atlantic Ocean perhaps in the Gulf of Mexico ( Canudas Gonzàlez, 1979 ) and off Florida (this study). Type locality: Sulu Sea.
